{"tid":748930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好傷心，工作真係可以麻醉自己","createTime":"2018-07-19T14:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T01:30:51.000Z","uid":157261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f76e86c762a6564ec4170805440ba5b062a5ae2","tid":748930,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"今日醫生話貓貓應該唔會活太耐<br />\n一路做野都冇咩野<br />\nOt到9點食飯就開始黎料<br />\n搭搭下車仲喊左出黎<br />\n而加仲係屋企樓下喊緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻貓好痴我<br />\n未病之前晚晚望住我刷牙<br />\n等我同佢按摩完先去訓覺<br />\n前排仲晚晚同我訓<br />\n平時我叫佢佢就會過黎好聽話<br />\n隻貓由小學開始陪我<br />\n中學大學到而加出黎做野<br />\n真係好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bd33a1d766372f4f47676cdb4670843b2337f2","tid":748930,"uid":133205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ec2554b8908ac48f024f81772706a4221ed52","tid":748930,"uid":135307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"養時就知會有呢一日<br />\n你已經陪咗佢一世<br />\n佢呢一世都好幸福"},{"pid":"430643d61c39e0ddad282b6ed7efa89c8f91a60c","tid":748930,"uid":157261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"細細個一齊玩一齊大<br />\n到變左屋企人咁<br />\n真係好難接受佢有一日真係要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee85a67230c4aa1c287361c434503f1bf524c10","tid":748930,"uid":135307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430643d61c39e0ddad282b6ed7efa89c8f91a60c","tid":748930,"uid":157261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"細細個一齊玩一齊大<br />\n到變左屋企人咁<br />\n真係好難接受佢有一日真係要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:30:51.000Z","msg":"明呀 我自己有養 不過佢依家仲細<br />\n我都唔敢諗有日無咗佢。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"